cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: Wexford County Council CCTV
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: *** Please upload all responses as a zip file. *** Wexford County Council requires to establish a single operator Framework Agreement for a security company licensed by the Private Security Authority (PSA) to provide the following services; Lot 1 - Extension to existing Town Centre CCTV System in Wexford Town. Lot 2 - Installation of a Town Centre CCTV System in New Ross. Lot 3 - Installation of a Town Centre CCTV System in Enniscorthy. Lot 4 - Installation of a Town Centre CCTV System in Bunclody.
